name: Closer?!
Lore: '''I''m going in closer to one of those big ones.'' ''Closer?!'' ''Closer?!'' ''Graarg?!''',
Text: 'During your move phase, use 1 Force to relocate one of your starships from a planet system to any related asteroid sector (or vice versa). This movement is free if a smuggler is on board. OR Cancel Rogue Asteroid or Close Call.',
